high_descs: turn right and walk until you pass the fridge on the left, and turn left to walk towards the white kitchen table at the end of the room
grab the loaf of bread off of the kitchen table
move to the left a bit and then face the refrigerator
place the bread inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
turn left and walk to the end of the room where the kitchen counter is
place the loaf of bread down on the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: place a cooled loaf of bread down on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn to the right and cross the room, then turn to the left to face the table.
Pick up the piece of bread that is next to the salt shaker on the edge of the table
Turn to the left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread on the shelf inside, then close the door for a few seconds before removing the bread from the refrigerator.
Turn to the left and walk to the counter.
Place the bread on the counter to the right of the potato.
anns.task_desc: To place a piece of cooled bread on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the table next to the fridge.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Go to the fridge on your right.
Chill the bread in the fridge and take it out.
Put the bread on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter by the sink.
